The paper focuses on object localization, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach involves deep learning and self-taught learning, which are also relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments are conducted on image datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
